Package edu.sru.thangiah.zeus.core Description

Contains the main data structures for Zeus. Contains the main data structure for Zeus. The first level is the depot linked list, which contains all the depots in the problem. Each depot contains a truck linked list which contains all the trucks in that depot. Each truck contains a nodes linked list, which contains all the nodes, or customers, that the truck services.
